Rainfall Prediction Web Application üå¶Ô∏è ->
An end-to-end machine learning project that predicts whether it will rain the next day. This application uses a Logistic Regression model trained on historical weather data and features a user-friendly web interface built with Streamlit that fetches live weather data using the OpenWeatherMap API.

üé• Live Demo
