‚ú® Features
Accurate Predictions: Utilizes a Logistic Regression model with 89.09% accuracy.

Live Weather Data: Integrates with the OpenWeatherMap API to fetch real-time weather data for any city.

User-Friendly Interface: A clean, accessible, and interactive web app built with Streamlit.

End-to-End Workflow: Covers the complete machine learning lifecycle from data cleaning and EDA to model deployment.

Secure API Key Handling: Uses Streamlit secrets management to keep the API key safe and secure.


üõ†Ô∏è Technologies Used
Programming Language: Python 3.10.11

Data Manipulation: Pandas, NumPy

Data Visualization: Matplotlib, Seaborn

Machine Learning: Scikit-learn, Logistic Regression Model

Web Framework: Streamlit

API Integration: Requests

Model Persistence: Joblib



‚öôÔ∏è Machine Learning Workflow
Data Cleaning: Handled missing values in the dataset by filling them with the mean or mode.

Exploratory Data Analysis (EDA): Visualized feature distributions and relationships to gain insights.

Feature Engineering: Converted categorical features (like WindGustDir and RainTomorrow) into a numerical format using one-hot encoding and mapping.

Model Training: Trained a Logistic Regression model on 80% of the data.

Model Evaluation: Achieved 89.09% accuracy on the 20% test set, validating the model performance.

Model Saving: The trained model was saved into a .joblib file for use in the web application.
